76561198049200785,Recommended,272510,12113679,"Posted: 15 September, 2014",all,foglower,"Woo this is a fun game. I say this game evens itself out. World Tournament mode is a thrill, and the Ninja Escapades which is basiclly story mode is entertaining... With a few fights in The Akatsuki Story, two fights in Shisui, and NONE in Obito's which I think is kind of lame. They do offer Free Battle mode, Online Mode, and World Tournament mode outside of the Ninja Escapdes mode though. World Tournament is a four man/woman battle. You start at D rank mode, and work your way up. First match is free for all, and after that you have to hunt down a partner on the tournament island to help you.edit add: So I just wanted to add I played 15 hours now, and found you can get mecha Naruto story if you beat world tournament the first time, and its highly worth it to seek out accessories if possible. You can make some pretty epic looks. In Free battles you can do League, and Survival mode. There is also a special type system ultimate, Drive, and awakening. Awakening allows for constant awakenings, Ultimate allows use of ultimate, and Drive makes you more interactive with allies, and they often protect you from ultimates. Bringing together allies on your team creates different effects. Naruto, Sasuke, and Sakura will get you the three way summon. So basiclly its based on who is on your team that makes the special and yes these specials replace your ultimate jutsu. So becareful cause your characters REAL ultimate might be better.Its got a good set up so far, and for those of you who are looking for a keyboard layout here is something just for you!Start: EnterBack: Right shiftY: AA: SpaceX: ZB: XLeft stick click: XRight stick click: right controlLeft back: QRight Back: ELeft trigger: WRight Trigger SLeft stick up: upLeft stick down: downLeft stick left: leftLeft stick right: rightRight stick up: TRight stick down: GRight stick left: FRight stick right: HDpad up: IDpad down: kDpad left: jDpad right: LIt works for me, and may be abit confusing, but basiclly it will work like...Q, and E for summoning partnersW for sub jutsuS for blockingA for chakraD for meleeZ for throwing ShurikenI,J,K,L are your itemsF,T,G,H, are your changing target in world tournament moment, or simply turning the camera.Oh and I forget to mention the space bar becomes your jump button.Enjoy this amazing game!"
