,Recommended,272510,31285984,Posted: 21 April,all,Zatchel,"A good game.Seems it got negative reviews mostly because the game hasnt changed that much from NSUNS3 to this, but I liked it all right since I hadnt buy the previous ones, it has a TON of characters and game modes and is fun for playing a versus match, the mechanics are simple enough to learn and the attacks are not complex, however the fighting system requires skill to master, its timing dependent.There is people online who use the most advantaged characters (for example, madara who has an insane range on his combo attack), but honestly, if you are skilled enough, that alone wont do. Its more important to time your attacks, counters and defense to chip on the enemy health.Overall I recommend it if you hadnt got the previous instalations as it is a fun game, however it will take a while to unlock all the characters."
